name: Unidentified_Yuuzhan_Vong_representative
content:
A Yuuzhan Vong made contact with the ruler of the Vagaari Empire, the Vagaari Miskara, by 23 ABY. In exchange for the Empire's help in the Yuuzhan Vong invasion of the galaxy, the Vagaari began incorporating the Yuuzhan Vong biotechnology.
The Yuuzhan Vong reprsentative was introduced in the 2010 sourcebook The Unknown Regions, published by Wizards of the Coast for the Star Wars Roleplaying Game.
